OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776859865
OL,3,CConcerns more people are buying
OL,4,Ccigarettes illegally on the black
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FInstead, it's thought smokers are
OL,8,Fopting for cheaper and riskier
OL,9,Falternatives.
OL,11,FRecent raids by Oxfordshire County
OL,12,FCouncil's Trading Standards team
OL,13,Funcovered illegal cigarettes, nicotine
OL,14,Fpouches, and vapes, often sold under
OL,15,Fthe counter.
OL,17,F"We seized about 7000 sticks of
OL,18,Fcigarettes, and about nine kilograms
OL,19,Fof illegal tobacco. That includes
OL,20,Fthings like rolling tobacco", said
OL,21,FOperations Manager, Davina Walkin.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776859865
OL,3,CConcerns more people are buying
OL,4,Ccigarettes illegally on the black
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"When you buy these products you're
OL,8,Factually supporting serious organised
OL,9,Fcrime because a lot of the people that
OL,10,Fare behind these organisations are the
OL,11,Fones that are doing human trafficking,
OL,12,Fmodern day slavery, that sort of
OL,13,Fthing."
OL,15,FOfficial data shows the number of
OL,16,Fcigarettes sold legally in the UK has
OL,17,Fdropped by 52% since 2021. And
OL,18,Falthough the number of smokers is also
OL,19,Fdeclining, the figures reveal this
OL,20,Fcan't be the only reason for the
OL,21,Fsudden drop in sales.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776859865
OL,3,CConcerns more people are buying
OL,4,Ccigarettes illegally on the black
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FDimpee Sood owns a convenience store
OL,8,Fin Portsmouth and says cheaper,
OL,9,Fillegal alternatives are more easily
OL,10,Faccessible than ever before, "The
OL,11,Fdecline has been significant, year on
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,F"Our sales have declined our purchases
OL,15,Ffor tobacco have declined. It is the
OL,16,Fcost.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776859865
OL,3,CConcerns more people are buying
OL,4,Ccigarettes illegally on the black
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"We're challenged by the rising cost
OL,8,Fof tobacco compared to the illicit
OL,9,Ftrade at a lot less price. We can't
OL,10,Fcompete at that and neither would we
OL,11,Fwant to."
OL,13,FThere are suggestions that higher
OL,14,Fprices, driven by rising tobacco
OL,15,Ftaxes, may be pushing more smokers
OL,16,Ftowards the black market.
OL,18,FBut according to charity Action on
OL,19,FSmoking and Health, it's more complex,
OL,20,Fpointing to a wider behavioural shift.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776859865
OL,3,CConcerns more people are buying
OL,4,Ccigarettes illegally on the black
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,F"We've got many more people who don't
OL,8,Fsmoke every day," said ASH chief
OL,9,Fexecutive, Hazel Cheeseman.
OL,11,F"They've substituted a lot of their
OL,12,Fcigarettes by vaping or using other
OL,13,Fnicotine products. And so that's a
OL,14,Freally big driver in this drop in
OL,15,Fconsumption that we've seen"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1776859865
OL,3,CConcerns more people are buying
OL,4,Ccigarettes illegally on the black
OL,5,Cmarket
OL,7,FThe government told ITV News, "The
OL,8,Fmain driver of declining tobacco duty
OL,9,Frevenue is less people smoking", and
OL,10,Fthat "taxing tobacco has helped nearly
OL,11,Fhalf of UK smokers quit smoking since
OL,12,F2011."
OL,14,FWith enforcement agencies determined
OL,15,Fto crack down, it's hoped the boom in
OL,16,Fthe black market might soon be stubbed
OL,17,Fout.
